These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, march, june, may, april, january, july
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
There 7 different types of food: corn, peas, raspberry, orange, mango, cherry, tomato
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
 2. the person eating mango is the dutch##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person eating raspberry##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating raspberry##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
11. the person eating corn is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the german##1
16. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
17. the person eating cherry is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Birthday      | march  | january        | april | june      | may     | february      | july     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Food         | raspberry | mango | corn | peas | tomato  | cherry  | orange    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

