.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, mirinda, tea
There 7 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, broccoli, pineapple, pumpkin, raspberry, strawberry
House: ranch-style, art-deco, modern, victorian, townhouse, tower, gothic-revival
City: miami, venice, paris, marseilles, prague, london, rome
 1. the person drinking cola is the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the victorian house is between the modern house and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the art-deco house is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the townhouse house is on the left of the tower house##1
13. the townhouse house is between the person eating strawberry and the tower house##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
15. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
16. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
20. the person eating broccoli is between the person traveling to london and the person eating artichoke##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
